Class NonActionableObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • new_simvasos.model.Abstract.SIMVASoS_Object
      • new_simvasos.model.Abstract.NonActionableObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CS_Knowledge, CS_Message, CS_Resource

    public abstract class NonActionableObject
extends SIMVASoS_Object
    Author:
    ymbaek Abstract class for every non-actionable object class in SIMVA-SoS. Actionable ojbects cannot perform any actions during the simulation, but the state or value can be accessed and modified by others. NonActionableObject only has its value (objectValue) as a specialized attribute.
